  "body_html": "<p>The Prodigy 3 is an all-mountain ski designed for supreme all-mountain enjoyment and durability in any conditions, making it ideal for both packed and powder snow. This intuitive, perfectly balanced, and stable ski features a 106 mm waist with Directional Twin shape and Elliptical Sidecut for user-friendly performance.</p>\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>106 mm waist width for versatile performance</li>\n  <li>Directional Twin shape for skiing and landing backwards</li>\n  <li>Elliptical Sidecut ensures user-friendly performance</li>\n  <li>Designed for both packed and powder snow conditions</li>\n  <li>Playful character suitable for buttering and pivoting</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Specifications</h3>\n<table>\n  <tr><td>Ski Size</td><td>164 cm</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Tip Width</td><td>133 mm</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Waist Width</td><td>106 mm</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Tail Width</td><td>125 mm</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Radius</td><td>15 m</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Weight Per Ski</td><td>1750 g</td></tr>\n</table>",
